member.summary:
Transforms x and y with the transformation matrix:
x1 = A*x + C*y + TX;
y1 = B*x + D*y + TY.

Scales x and y with the transformation matrix:
x1 = A*x + C*y;
y1 = B*x + D*y.

member.remarks:
Note: following Font types are supported for saving:
New TTF Fonts;
TTF Font subsets;
CFF Font subsets;
Type1 Font subsets.

